OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a bright day with a
OL,6,Ffew showers around, the odd one could
OL,7,Fbe heavy and thundery. Best of the
OL,8,Fsunshine across the west coast and
OL,9,FHebrides.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA bright end to the day with
OL,12,Fscattered showers, these will die out
OL,13,Fin the east leading to a dry night
OL,14,Fwith clear spells. Cloudy in west with
OL,15,Ffurther showers.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FIt will be another day of
OL,18,Fbright spells and showers, some
OL,19,Fperhaps heavy and thundery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
