OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FCloudy with rain or drizzle on
OL,7,FThursday. Bright spells and scattered
OL,8,Fshowers on Friday then dry with sunny
OL,9,Fspells on Saturday.
